<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_138" id="68r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_138_r2l11"><expan>Dıeth<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Lantſchad <expan>vıcʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Aſchaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_138_r2l12"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>vıcʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> als vns eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l13">Yoſep Pücʒels des Juden ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> beg </del> Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l14">Vnd <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu lıeb </del> . <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Yoſeps weıb vnd kınden vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l15"><expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒweyen <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Dauid vnd <expan>ſelıgma<ex>n</ex></expan> den Juden / das geleyt / daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l16">Jn eẅch ʒu lıeb vor bey vns <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haben . <expan>erleng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . ſand </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l17">Mıchels tag ſchıerıſt in <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> maſſ / als vor auf Jacobȷ <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> VVıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l18">wol vns das doch etwas ſwer ıſt vnd <expan>lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v̈berhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geweſen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l19"><expan>Hett<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ewer <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> darinn nıht <expan>angeſehe<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd getrawen dıe <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l20">Juden . <expan>ſüll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des yoſeps ſache in derʒeıt <expan>auſʒtrage<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ nıht not ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l21">vns mer <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu <expan>bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l22"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>D<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Petrj et Paulȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_138" id="68r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Dieth<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Lantschad, <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        zu <expan>Aschaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> aber
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt, von Yosep Püczels des juden sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Yoseps weib und kinden und
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> zweyen
                            <expan>brud<ex>er</ex>n</expan> David und
                            <expan>Seligma<ex>n</ex></expan> den juden das geleyt, daz wir in ewch
                        zu lieb vor bey uns <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haben,
                                <expan>erleng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hiezwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <app>
<note><q type="date">sand Michels tag schierist</q>29.09.1420</note>
</app> in <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> mass, als vor auf Jacobi
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>, wie wol uns das doch etwas
                        swer ist, und <expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>überhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gewesen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>,
                                <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewer
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> darinn niht
                            <expan>angesehe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und getrawen die
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> juden
                            <expan>süll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des Yoseps sache in derzeit
                                <expan>ausztrage<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz niht not sey uns mer
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu <expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Petri et Pauli.</ab>
</div>
